{"tid":297489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Celine爸爸譚順生為國力學生 1年極速博士畢業疑偽造文書","createTime":"2017-06-25T13:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-25T18:24:42.000Z","uid":15440,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77824468bb56b27c7a841c32b5e5b0cf00782f8d","tid":297489,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/213820_6bf4e81de98f2999f7ea242ae189d6c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F213820_6bf4e81de98f2999f7ea242ae189d6c2.jpg&h=b6636611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9歲女童Celine自因全美一叮爆紅後，其父譚順生一直是非纏身，更有人質疑其博士銜頭真確性，他為證清白，今午在記者會上出示菲律賓科技大學（NEUST）的博士畢業證書，指自己確實曾修讀「Doctor of Philosophy in Business Administration」，又聲稱自己修讀兩年始取得證書。但本報調查發現，譚在2008年經國力書院報讀相關課程，並於同年畢業，較同期畢業同學提前一至兩年。消息人士指，譚極可能與其他涉及國力書院的人士一樣，涉偽造文書，推前入學日期（Backdate）。<br />\n<br />\n國力書院早前被揭於香港代辦菲律賓比立勤國立大學及太歷國立大學之海外課程，涉嫌為部分申請人偽造文書，將入學日推前，以取得該等菲律賓大學的學士、碩士及博士學位，藝人蔡思貝及民建聯區議員鄭琴淵等人亦被揭發為國力書院的學生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170625&amp;guid=56875486&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170625%26guid%3D56875486%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=xBA6bw5xIs3RfQOG8am6Le9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=ab8dd6d1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170625%26guid%3D56875486%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=089e8421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170625&amp;guid=56875486&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"e1d7bd9f193c919651286bcc446d405f62614db4","tid":297489,"uid":84494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:39:35.000Z","msg":"唔理真定假 推一推先"},{"pid":"168cfeded4dc30174e50